edu.ucla.sspace.common

Class VectorMapSemanticSpace<T extends Vector>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ucla.sspace.common.VectorMapSemanticSpace<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SemanticSpace, Serializable

    public class VectorMapSemanticSpace<T extends Vector>
extends Object
implements SemanticSpace, Serializable
    This SemanticSpace wraps a Map from strings to Vectors. Both processDocument(java.io.BufferedReader) and processSpace(java.util.Properties) are no-ops.
    Author:
    Keith Stevens
    See Also:
